    "body": "The current tests for `importdescriptors` RPC do not check for cases where RPC errors should be thrown.\r\n\r\nThis PR adds coverage for _importing a descriptor when the wallet is encrypted_ and for _importing a descriptor while the wallet is rescanning_ \r\n\r\nFor context, this lack of coverage was found while implementing #34861 when a reviewer found that this was being silently broken in the PR.\r\n\r\nI am not sure if the \"rescanning test\" approach is the optimal solution, I am open to suggestions.",
